            "content": "# Right Sidebar Panel Design\n\n**Date:** 2026-04-17\n**Feature:** OpenCode-style right info panel\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nAdd a persistent right sidebar panel to the agent-tui TUI that displays:\n- Context section with token count and usage percentage\n- Activated MCP servers list\n- Modified files during the session\n- Active project path and branch\n- CLI name and version\n\n---\n\n## Design Decisions\n\n| Decision | Value |\n|----------|-------|\n| Width | 200px (narrow) |\n| Visibility | Toggleable (Ctrl+M) |\n| Auto-hide | On terminals < 80 columns |\n| File tracking | Automatic (via tool calls) |\n| Border | 4px solid $primary for clear separation |\n\n---\n\n## Layout Structure\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┬──────────────────┐\n│                                     │ Context          │\n│                                     │ 8.2K   45%       │\n│     Main Chat Area                  │ [=======-----]   │\n│                                     │                  │\n│                                     │ Activated MCP    │\n│                                     │ ● filesystem     │\n│                                     │ ● github         │\n│                                     │ ○ memory         │\n│                                     │                  │\n│                                     │ Modified Files   │\n│                                     │ + new.py         │\n│                                     │ ~ existing.rs    │\n│                                     │ • README.md      │\n│                                     │                  │\n│                                     │──────────────────│\n│                                     │ ~/REPOS/...:main │\n│                                     │ agent-tui v1.2.3 │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┴──────────────────┘\n            ← 4px border ($primary) →\n```\n\n---\n\n## Sections\n\n### 1. Context\n- Token count (formatted: 8.2K, 1.2M, etc.)\n- Usage percentage (45%)\n- Progress bar visualization\n- Source: existing token tracking from StatusBar\n\n### 2. Activated MCP\n- List of connected MCP servers\n- Status indicator: ● connected (green), ○ disconnected (muted)\n- Shows server name only (not individual tools)\n- Source: MCPToolManager or equivalent\n\n### 3. Modified Files\n- Files created (+), modified (~), or touched (•) during session\n- Automatic tracking via tool call events (EditFile, WriteFile, etc.)\n- Scrollable if list exceeds available space\n- Color coding:\n  - `+` green: created\n  - `~` amber: modified\n  - `•` muted: touched/read\n\n### 4. Bottom Info (Footer)\n- Project path with branch: `~/REPOS/agent-tui:main`\n- Uses `~` for home directory\n- CLI name and version: `agent-tui v1.2.3`\n- Separated by 1px border-top\n\n---\n\n## Technical Approach\n\n### Widget\nCreate new `InfoPanel` widget in `entrypoints/widgets/` extending `Static`.\n\n### Layout Integration\n- Add to `app.py` `compose()` alongside existing widgets\n- Use `dock: right` to position\n- Toggle visibility via Ctrl+M binding (reuse `toggle_mcp_panel` or new)\n- Auto-hide logic on terminal resize event\n\n### File Tracking\n- Hook into existing tool call events\n- Track files from: `EditFile`, `WriteFile`, `CreateFile`, `ReadFile` tools\n- Maintain in-memory list during session\n- Clear on new session\n\n### State Management\n- Reactive properties for each section\n- Updates flow from existing app state (tokens, MCP servers, etc.)\n\n---\n\n## CSS Classes\n\n```css\nInfoPanel {\n    width: 200;\n    height: 100%;\n    dock: right;\n    background: $surface;\n    border-left: solid $primary;\n}\n\nInfoPanel .info-header { }\nInfoPanel .info-context { }\nInfoPanel .info-mcp { }\nInfoPanel .info-files { }\nInfoPanel .info-footer { }\n```\n\n---\n\n## Toggle Behavior\n\n- **Ctrl+M** toggles panel visibility\n- Panel state persists during session\n- Auto-shows when terminal width >= 80 columns on startup\n- Auto-hides when terminal shrinks below 80 columns\n\n---\n\n## Edge Cases\n\n1. **Narrow terminal (< 80 cols):** Panel hidden by default\n2. **No MCP servers:** Show \"No MCP servers\" placeholder\n3. **No modified files:** Show \"No files modified\" placeholder\n4. **Long file paths:** Truncate with ellipsis, show full path on hover\n5. **Zero tokens:** Hide context section until first token count received",
